            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Pulsator accipet <note>sic</note> lamnas LXXX <lb n="2"/>imbrices murales <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>umero</ex></expan> XX <lb n="3"/>qu&amp;lt;in=NI&amp;gt;os dodrantes <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>umero</ex></expan> XX <lb n="4"/>sextum Kalandas <note>sic</note> Augustas <lb n="5"/>Iustius Optatus accipet <note>sic</note> <lb n="6"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><expan><abbr>A</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><expan><abbr>S</abbr><ex cert="low"/>T</expan><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>se</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan><supplied reason="lost">c</supplied>undarias <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>umero</ex></expan> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="8"/>lamnas <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>umero</ex></expan> XII <lb n="9"/>inbrices <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>umero</ex></expan> XXX <lb n="10"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">--</supplied>ttus Augusti <lb n="11"/>venit ad nos XV <expan><abbr>Kal</abbr><ex>endas</ex></expan> <lb n="12"/>Augustas 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Bodenziegel eines Hypokaustraumes. Schreibtechnik: Graffito; vor dem Brand eingeritzt. Kursive Buchstaben. Textwiedergabe nach Rothenhöfer.</p>
            </div>
